Walgreens, Alliance Boots Finalize Merger  

            Submitted by manyeshab on Wed, 12/31/2014 - 13:26    

Walgreen Co. and Alliance Boots have finalized their two-step merger launched in 2012 to form Walgreens Boots Alliance—marketed as the world's first global pharmacy-led health and well-being enterprise.  



Walgreens, Alliance Boots Partner

            Submitted by manyeshab on Tue, 06/19/2012 - 14:11    

Drugstore chain Walgreen Co. and international pharmacy-led health and beauty group Alliance Boots have partnered to create what they’re calling the first global pharmacy-led, health and well-being enterprise.
 













 


